friends in local multiplayer mode, adding an extra layer of excitement to the chaos. Who will emerge as the ultimate delivery daredevil?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/542bf4bd81363a08750d996020930f74.poster.avif?t=1737126588\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/542bf4bd81363a08750d996020930f74.webm?t=1737126588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/542bf4bd81363a08750d996020930f74.mp4?t=1737126588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>Single player story mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a young racer seeking revenge against the one responsible for their downfall. Take on daring missions to uncover the mastermind behind the chaos and the destruction of innocent lives. With upgrades, strategy, and skill, conquer the streets, become the ultimate delivery champion, and bring this mayhem to an end!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/04c88f40cedc4f74a95ede1f0103fa0f.poster.avif?t=1737126588\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/04c88f40cedc4f74a95ede1f0103fa0f.webm?t=1737126588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745550/extras/04c88f40cedc4f74a95ede1f0103fa0f.mp4?t=1737126588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
